If you had a Vanagon I would recommend the lockable enclosed 
luggage box like I have. Its made of fiderglass and looks a 
lot like one of those wind deflector things you see on 18 
wheelers. Check our www.vanagon.org and click on "Bagawest"

Thanks,
Chris 

